DashboardDefinitionComponents.Name: User Projects
DashboardDefinitionComponents.Parameters:
[{"WidgetSubTitle":"Different Projects the User was or is involved in","WidgetType":"grid","WidgetFilterField":"","WidgetColor":"","WidgetFrameStyle":{},"WidgetXPosition":0,"WidgetYPosition":38,"WidgetRows":24,"WidgetColumns":48,"WidgetHeader":{"showContextInfo":false,"WidgetPeriodChooser":{"type":"year","visible":false},"WidgetMetrics":{"visible":false,"Metrics":[{"visible":false,"metricName":"# Forecast","metricFieldValue":"TimeGrandTotal"},{"visible":false,"metricName":"# Actual","metricFieldValue":"UtilizationPercentGrandTotal"}]},"showSubTitle":true,"showTitle":true},"WidgetDataSources":{"main":{"type":"querytext","value":"WITH UsersCapacity AS
(
	SELECT 
		u.Oid AS UserId,
		(
			(
				(
					(DATEDIFF(dd, @FromDate, @ToDate) + 1)
					-(DATEDIFF(wk, @FromDate, @ToDate) * 2)
					-(CASE WHEN DATENAME(dw, @FromDate) = 'Sunday' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
					-(CASE WHEN DATENAME(dw, @ToDate) = 'Saturday' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
				) + 1 
			)
			-
			(
				(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Analytics.DatamartLeave dl WHERE dl.UserId = u.Oid AND dl.[Date] BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate)
				+
				(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Analytics.DatamartHoliday dh WHERE dh.UserId = u.Oid AND dh.[Date] BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate)
			)
		) * u.RequiredHours AS WorkingHours,
		(SELECT ISNULL(SUM(dl.[Hours]), 0.0) FROM Analytics.DatamartLeave dl WHERE dl.UserId = u.Oid AND dl.[Date] BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AS Leaves,
		(SELECT ISNULL(SUM(dh.[Hours]), 0.0) FROM Analytics.DatamartHoliday dh WHERE dh.UserId = u.Oid AND dh.[Date] BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) as Holidays
	FROM
		[User] u
	WHERE
		u.Oid = @UserOid
),
UsersHours AS
(
	SELECT
		dt.ClientGroup,
		dt.Client,
		dt.[UserId],
		dt.[User],
		dt.Project,
		dt.ProjectClassificationName,
		dt.ProjectTypeName,
		dt.[Job],
		SUM(dt.ActualTime) AS [Hours],
		SUM(dt.AdministrativeTime) AS [AdministrativeHours],
		SUM(ISNULL(dt.InternalWorkTime, 0.0)) AS [InternalWorkHours],
		SUM(dt.NewBusinessTime) AS [NewBusinessHours],
		SUM(dt.BillableTime) AS [BillableHours],
		SUM(ISNULL(dt.BillableTime, 0.0) - ISNULL(dt.[AdministrativeTime], 0.0)) as [ClientHours],
		SUM(ISNULL(dt.[ActualTime] - (dt.[AdministrativeTime] + dt.[NewBusinessTime] + dt.[BillableTime]), 0.0)) as [NonWorkedHours]
	FROM 
		Analytics.DatamartTimesheet/*(@CurrentUserId)*/ dt
	WHERE
		dt.[Date] BETWEEN @FromDate and DateAdd(d, -1, @ToDate)
		AND dt.UserId = @UserOid
	GROUP BY
		dt.ClientGroup,
		dt.Client,
		dt.[UserId],
		dt.[User],
		dt.Project,
		dt.ProjectClassificationName,
		dt.ProjectTypeName,
        dt.[Job]
)
SELECT 
	uh.ClientGroup,
	uh.Client,
	uh.[User],
	uh.Project,
	uh.ProjectClassificationName,
	IIF(uh.ProjectTypeName = '', 'Admin', uh.ProjectTypeName) as ProjectTypeName,
	uh.Job,
	uh.[Hours],
	uh.AdministrativeHours,
	uh.InternalWorkHours,
	uh.NewBusinessHours,
	uh.BillableHours,
	uh.ClientHours,
	uh.NonWorkedHours,
	0 AS Capacity,
	0 AS Leaves,
	IIF(uc.WorkingHours > 0, ISNULL(uh.[BillableHours], 0.0) / uc.WorkingHours, 1.0) as UtilizationPercentage,
	IIF(uc.WorkingHours > 0, ISNULL(uh.[NewBusinessHours], 0.0) / uc.WorkingHours, 1.0) as UtilizationNonBillablePercentage
FROM 
	UsersHours uh,
	UsersCapacity uc
WHERE
	uh.UserId = uc.UserId
UNION ALL
SELECT 
	'' as ClientGroup,
	'' as Client,
	'' as [User],
	'' as Project,
	'' as ProjectClassificationName,
	'Leave' as ProjectTypeName,
	'' as Job,
	uc.Leaves as [Hours],
	0 as AdministrativeHours,
	0 as InternalWorkHours,
	0 as NewBusinessHours,
	0 as BillableHours,
	0 as ClientHours,
	0 as NonWorkedHours,
	uc.WorkingHours AS Capacity,
	uc.Leaves AS Leaves,
	0 as UtilizationPercentage,
	0 as UtilizationNonBillablePercentage
FROM 
	UsersCapacity uc"}},"Filters":{},"QueryConfiguration":{"RequiredFilters":["startDate","endDate","userOid"]}}]

DashboardDefinitionComponents.Name: Utilization per User
DashboardDefinitionComponents.Parameters:
[{"WidgetSubTitle":"Billable and Non-Billable Actual Hours in % of User Capacity","WidgetType":"grid","WidgetFilterField":"","WidgetColor":"","WidgetFrameStyle":{},"WidgetXPosition":0,"WidgetYPosition":21,"WidgetRows":17,"WidgetColumns":48,"WidgetHeader":{"showContextInfo":false,"WidgetPeriodChooser":{"type":"year","visible":false},"WidgetMetrics":{"visible":false,"Metrics":[{"visible":false,"metricName":"# Forecast","metricFieldValue":"TimeGrandTotal"},{"visible":false,"metricName":"# Actual","metricFieldValue":"UtilizationPercentGrandTotal"}]},"showSubTitle":true,"showTitle":true},"WidgetDataSources":{"main":{"type":"querytext","value":"WITH UsersCapacity AS
(
	SELECT 
		u.Oid AS UserId,
		u.[Name] as [User], 
		u.UserType,
		(
			(
				(
					(DATEDIFF(dd, IIF(@FromDate > u.StartDate, @FromDate, u.StartDate), IIF(@ToDate > u.ExpirationDate, u.ExpirationDate, @ToDate)) + 1)
					-(DATEDIFF(wk, IIF(@FromDate > u.StartDate, @FromDate, u.StartDate), IIF(@ToDate > u.ExpirationDate, u.ExpirationDate, @ToDate)) * 2)
					-(CASE WHEN DATENAME(dw, IIF(@FromDate > u.StartDate, @FromDate, u.StartDate)) = 'Sunday' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
					-(CASE WHEN DATENAME(dw, IIF(@ToDate > u.ExpirationDate, u.ExpirationDate, @ToDate)) = 'Saturday' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
				) + 1 
			)
			-
			(
				(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Analytics.DatamartLeave dl WHERE dl.UserId = u.Oid AND dl.[Date] BETWEEN IIF(@FromDate > u.StartDate, @FromDate, u.StartDate) AND IIF(@ToDate > u.ExpirationDate, u.ExpirationDate, @ToDate))
				+
				(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Analytics.DatamartHoliday dh WHERE dh.UserId = u.Oid AND dh.[Date] BETWEEN IIF(@FromDate > u.StartDate, @FromDate, u.StartDate) AND IIF(@ToDate > u.ExpirationDate, u.ExpirationDate, @ToDate))
			)
		) * u.RequiredHours AS WorkingHours,
		(SELECT ISNULL(SUM(dh.[Hours]), 0.0) FROM Analytics.DatamartHoliday dh WHERE dh.UserId = u.Oid AND dh.[Date] BETWEEN IIF(@FromDate > u.StartDate, @FromDate, u.StartDate) AND IIF(@ToDate > u.ExpirationDate, u.ExpirationDate, @ToDate)) as Holidays
	FROM
		[User] u
	WHERE
		(u.Company = @CompanyOid or @CompanyOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
		AND (u.Division = @DivisionOid or @DivisionOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
		AND (u.Department = @DepartmentOid or @DepartmentOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
),
UsersHours AS
(
	SELECT
		v.Department,
		v.UserTypologyGroup,	
		v.[UserId],
		SUM(v.[Hours]) AS [Hours],
		SUM(v.[AdministrativeHours]) AS [AdministrativeHours],
		SUM(v.[InternalWorkHours]) AS [InternalWorkHours],
		SUM(v.[NewBusinessHours]) AS [NewBusinessHours],
		SUM(v.[BillableHours]) AS [BillableHours],
		SUM(v.[ClientHours]) as [ClientHours],
		SUM(v.[NonWorkedHours]) as [NonWorkedHours],
		SUM(v.Leaves) as Leaves
	FROM
	(
	SELECT
		dt.Department,
		dt.UserTypologyGroup,	
		dt.[UserId],
		SUM(dt.ActualTime) AS [Hours],
		SUM(dt.AdministrativeTime) AS [AdministrativeHours],
		SUM(ISNULL(dt.InternalWorkTime, 0.0)) AS [InternalWorkHours],
		SUM(dt.NewBusinessTime) AS [NewBusinessHours],
		SUM(dt.BillableTime) AS [BillableHours],
		SUM(ISNULL(dt.BillableTime, 0.0) - ISNULL(dt.[AdministrativeTime], 0.0)) as [ClientHours],
		SUM(ISNULL(dt.[ActualTime] - (dt.[AdministrativeTime] + dt.[NewBusinessTime] + dt.[BillableTime]), 0.0)) as [NonWorkedHours],
		0 as Leaves
	FROM 
		Analytics.DatamartTimesheet/*(@CurrentUserId)*/ dt
	WHERE
        dt.[Date] between @FromDate and @ToDate
		AND (dt.CompanyId = @CompanyOid or @CompanyOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
		AND (dt.DivisionId = @DivisionOid or @DivisionOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
		AND (dt.DepartmentId = @DepartmentOid or @DepartmentOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
	GROUP BY
		dt.Department,
		dt.UserTypologyGroup,	
		dt.[UserId]
	UNION ALL
	SELECT
		dl.Department,
		dl.UserTypologyGroup,	
		dl.[UserId],
		0 AS [Hours],
		0 AS [AdministrativeHours],
		0 AS [InternalWorkHours],
		0 AS [NewBusinessHours],
		0 AS [BillableHours],
		0 as [ClientHours],
		0 as [NonWorkedHours],
		SUM(dl.[Hours]) AS Leaves
	FROM 
		Analytics.DatamartLeave/*(@CurrentUserId)*/ dl
	WHERE
        dl.[Date] between @FromDate and @ToDate
		AND (dl.CompanyId = @CompanyOid or @CompanyOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
		AND (dl.DivisionId = @DivisionOid or @DivisionOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
		AND (dl.DepartmentId = @DepartmentOid or @DepartmentOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
	GROUP BY
		dl.Department,
		dl.UserTypologyGroup,	
		dl.[UserId]
	) v
	GROUP BY
		v.Department,
		v.UserTypologyGroup,	
		v.[UserId]
)
SELECT 
	uh.Department,
	uh.UserTypologyGroup,
	uc.[User],
	ut.[Name] as UserType,
	uh.UserId,
	uh.[Hours],
	uh.AdministrativeHours,
	uh.InternalWorkHours,
	uh.NewBusinessHours,
	uh.BillableHours,
	uh.ClientHours,
	uh.NonWorkedHours,
	uc.WorkingHours AS Capacity,
	uh.Leaves AS Leaves,
	IIF(uc.WorkingHours > 0, ISNULL(uh.[BillableHours], 0.0) / uc.WorkingHours, 1.0) as UtilizationPercentage,
	IIF(uc.WorkingHours > 0, ISNULL(uh.[NewBusinessHours], 0.0) / uc.WorkingHours, 1.0) as UtilizationNonBillablePercentage
FROM 
	UsersHours uh,
	UsersCapacity uc
	LEFT OUTER JOIN UserType ut ON (ut.Oid = uc.UserType)
WHERE
	uh.UserId = uc.UserId
	AND (uc.UserType = @UserType or @UserType = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
"}},"Filters":{},"QueryConfiguration":{"RequiredFilters":["startDate","endDate","CompanyOid","DivisionOid","DepartmentOid"]}}]

DashboardDefinitionComponents.Name: Utilization per Client
DashboardDefinitionComponents.Parameters:
[{"WidgetSubTitle":"Actual Hours per Client in % of Total","WidgetType":"chart","WidgetFilterField":"","WidgetColor":"#dddddd","WidgetFrameStyle":{},"WidgetXPosition":0,"WidgetYPosition":10,"WidgetRows":11,"WidgetColumns":16,"WidgetHeader":{"showContextInfo":false,"WidgetPeriodChooser":{"type":"year","visible":false},"WidgetMetrics":{"visible":false,"Metrics":[{"visible":true,"metricName":"# Planned","metricFieldValue":"PlannedTimeGrandTotal"}]},"showSubTitle":true,"showTitle":true},"WidgetDataSources":{"main":{"type":"querytext","value":"with userType as (
	SELECT
		v.Oid,
		v.UserTypeId
	FROM 
		Analytics.DatamartUser v
	GROUP BY
		v.Oid,
		v.UserTypeId
)
SELECT	top 10
		v.Client,
		(v.[Hours] / IIF(v.[TotalHours] > 0, v.[TotalHours], 1.0)) as UtilizationPercentage
FROM	
(
	SELECT
			v.Client,	
			SUM(v.BillableTime) as [Hours],
			SUM(SUM(v.BillableTime)) OVER () as [TotalHours]
	FROM
			Analytics.DatamartTimesheet/*(@CurrentUserId)*/ v, userType ut
	WHERE	
			(v.CompanyId = @CompanyOid or @CompanyOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
			AND (v.DivisionId = @DivisionOid or @DivisionOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
			AND (v.DepartmentId = @DepartmentOid or @DepartmentOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
			AND v.UserId = ut.Oid 
			AND (ut.UserTypeId = @UserType or @UserType = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
			AND v.[Date] between @FromDate and @ToDate
	GROUP BY
			v.Client
) v
ORDER BY (v.[Hours] / IIF(v.[TotalHours] > 0, v.[TotalHours], 1.0)) desc
","mapping":""}},"Filters":{},"QueryConfiguration":{"RequiredFilters":["startDate","endDate","CompanyOid","DivisionOid","DepartmentOid","UserType"]}}]

DashboardDefinitionComponents.Name: Period Selector
DashboardDefinitionComponents.Parameters:
[{"WidgetSubTitle":"Closed and In Progress Tickets","WidgetType":"rangeselector","WidgetFilterField":"","WidgetColor":"#efefef","WidgetFrameStyle":{},"WidgetXPosition":0,"WidgetYPosition":2,"WidgetRows":8,"WidgetColumns":48,"WidgetHeader":{"WidgetPeriodChooser":{"type":"year","visible":false},"showSubTitle":false,"showTitle":true},"WidgetDataSources":{"main":{"type":"querytext","value":"With Dates as
(
	SELECT 
		cast(concat(@year, '-1', '-1') as date) as [StartDate],
		cast(concat(@year, '-12', '-31') as date) as [EndDate]
),
AllDays as 
( 
	select   
		d.StartDate as [Date], 
		1 as [level]
	from Dates d
    union all
	select   
		DATEADD(DAY, 1, [Date]), [level] + 1
	from     
		AllDays, Dates d
	where    
		[Date] < d.EndDate 
),
UserType as (
	SELECT
		v.Oid,
		v.UserTypeId
	FROM 
		Analytics.DatamartUser v
	GROUP BY
		v.Oid,
		v.UserTypeId
),
GetData as (
	SELECT
		SUM(v.[Hours]) as [Hours],
		v.[Date]
	FROM
	(
		SELECT 
			IsNull(SUM(v.ActualTime), 0) as [Hours],
			v.[Date] as [Date]
		FROM
			Analytics.DatamartTimesheet/*(@CurrentUserId)*/ v, userType ut
		WHERE	
			(Year(v.[Date]) = @year) 
			and (v.CompanyId = @CompanyOid or @CompanyOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
			and (v.DivisionId = @DivisionOid or @DivisionOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
			and (v.DepartmentId = @DepartmentOid or @DepartmentOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
			and v.UserId = ut.Oid 
			and (ut.UserTypeId = @UserType or @UserType = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
		GROUP BY
			v.[Date]
		UNION ALL
		SELECT 
			IsNull(SUM(v.[Hours]), 0) as [Hours],
			v.[Date] as [Date]
		FROM
			Analytics.DatamartLeave/*(@CurrentUserId)*/ v, userType ut
		WHERE	
			(Year(v.[Date]) = @year) 
			and (v.CompanyId = @CompanyOid or @CompanyOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
			and (v.DivisionId = @DivisionOid or @DivisionOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
			and (v.DepartmentId = @DepartmentOid or @DepartmentOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
			and v.UserId = ut.Oid 
			and (ut.UserTypeId = @UserType or @UserType = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
		GROUP BY
			v.[Date]
		UNION ALL
		SELECT 
			IsNull(SUM(v.[Hours]), 0) as [Hours],
			v.[Date] as [Date]
		FROM
			Analytics.DatamartHoliday/*(@CurrentUserId)*/ v, userType ut
		WHERE	
			(Year(v.[Date]) = @year) 
			and (v.CompanyId = @CompanyOid or @CompanyOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
			and (@DivisionOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' or v.DepartmentId = (select d.Division from Department d where d.Oid = @DepartmentOid))
			and (v.DepartmentId = @DepartmentOid or @DepartmentOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
			and v.UserId = ut.Oid 
			and (ut.UserTypeId = @UserType or @UserType = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
		GROUP BY
			v.[Date]
	) v 
	GROUP BY
		v.[Date]
)
select 
	ad.[Date],
	sum(IsNull(gd.[Hours], 0)) as [Hours] 
from
	AllDays ad
		left outer join GetData gd on cast(gd.[Date] as date) = cast(ad.[Date] as date)
group by 
	ad.[Date]
option 
	(MAXRECURSION 0)","mapping":""}},"Filters":{},"QueryConfiguration":{"RequiredFilters":["year","CompanyOid","DivisionOid","DepartmentOid","UserType"]}}]
